args: Ugh, I can't believe I overslept.\nWhat am I going to do?!
Ooof. Oh, wow. Are you okay?
Er, right. Sorry about that.\nYou aren't hurt, are you?
Huh?! Um...no! No, I think I'm fine.
Well, that's good news, at least.\nDo you want me to help you up?
Th-thanks. That's very nice of you.
Oh wow, you're handsome... There's such\na noble air about you...
Sorry, I didn't quite catch that.
You're kind of spacing out there. You didn't\nhit your head or something, did you?
I finally found you... You're my soul mate!
All this time, I've been on a journey to\nfind my soul mate.
But now my journey is finally over,\nbecause I've found who I was looking for!
Ah, I knew it would all pay off in the end...\nYou're everything I dreamed of!
Would you mind maybe filling me in on\nwhat's going on?
I get that you were on a journey, but when\nyou say soul mate, you don't literally—
I mean that we're going to get married\nand live happily ever after! ...Duh-doy.
Of course! My heart is telling me you're\nthe one—AND we met just like I thought\nwe would!
This can only be destiny at work.
So let's start dating! Oh, and planning the\nwedding, of course. We'll need jesters and\na band and bears on unicycles and—
Okay, slow down. You can't just throw\nsomething like that at a person. I mean,\nI don't even KNOW you.
Pffft! Details. We can get to know one\nanother as we go along.
Like, what's your name, for example?
Today is such a WONDERFUL day!
Er, I'm not actually a knight so much as a\nprince. Although I DO have a sword,\nso maybe that...
Look, we're getting sidetracked. You really\nshouldn't treat marriage so flippan—
You're a PRINCE?! Eeeeeeeee!\nYou just got a thousand times dreamier!
Oh my gosh, this really IS fate at work!\nNow let's go, my dear Prince Charming!
To your house, of course! Or your castle,\nI suppose, since you're royalty and all.
But wherever you live, just know that I'll\nbe by your side forever.
Will you PLEASE listen to me?!
Hee hee! I wonder when we should hold\nthe ceremony? Fall weddings are nice...
I can hardly wait to be up there on the\naltar with you. Ahh...
